---
const zonas = [
  "Lanús",
  "Avellaneda",
  "Lomas de Zamora",
  "Quilmes",
  "Banfield",
  "CABA",
  "Zona Sur",
  "Zona Oeste",
  "Zona Norte",
  "La Plata",
  "Mar del Plata",
  "Todas las provincias",
];
---

<section id="cobertura" class="coverage section">
  <div class="container coverage__inner">
    <div class="coverage__content">
      <span class="eyebrow">Cobertura</span>
      <h2>Operamos en todo el AMBA y todas las provincias.</h2>
      <p class="coverage__lead">
        Base en Lanús, salidas diarias por Buenos Aires y traslados de larga distancia coordinados
        para todo el país. Si tu destino no aparece en la lista, consultanos: probablemente vamos.
      </p>

      <ul class="coverage__zones">
        {zonas.map((z) => <li>{z}</li>)}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <aside class="coverage__card">
      <h3>Base operativa</h3>
      <p class="coverage__addr">
        Mendoza 2765<br />
        Lanús, Buenos Aires
      </p>

      <iframe
        src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Mendoza+2765,+Lan%C3%BAs,+Buenos+Aires&output=embed"
        title="Ubicación Transporte Gioia e Hijos"
        loading="lazy"
        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
      ></iframe>

      <a
        class="coverage__link"
        href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Mendoza+2765,+Lan%C3%BAs,+Buenos+Aires"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
      >
        Ver en Google Maps →
      </a>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .coverage {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .coverage__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .coverage__content h2 {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .coverage__lead {
    color: var(--gris-700);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .coverage__zones {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .coverage__zones li {
    background: var(--gris-100);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--gris-200);
  }

  .coverage__card {
    background: var(--gris-100);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gris-200);
  }

  .coverage__card h3 {
    color: var(--bordo);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .coverage__addr {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .coverage__card iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 240px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .coverage__link {
    color: var(--bordo);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .coverage__link:hover {
    color: var(--bordo-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .coverage__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
